{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 68,
    "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
    "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 52,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 5272,
        "text": "努奈[阿拉伯语一个字母的音译，唯安拉最知道其意]。以笔和他们[天使在功过簿中]所记录的发誓！",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5273,
        "text": "以你的主的恩惠发誓！你[穆圣]绝不是疯子。",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5274,
        "text": "你必将获得永恒的报酬。",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5275,
        "text": "你的确具有伟大的品德。",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5276,
        "text": "你不久将看见，他们不久也将看见，",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5277,
        "text": "你们中谁是疯子。",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5278,
        "text": "你的主的确最知道谁迷失了他[安拉]的道[伊斯兰教]，也最知道谁是遵行正道者。",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5279,
        "text": "你不要服从否认者[否认伊斯兰教，穆圣和《古兰经》]。",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5280,
        "text": "他们希望你[在伊斯兰教上向他们]妥协，以便他们也[向你]妥协。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5281,
        "text": "你不要服从每个常发誓者——这种发誓是毫无价值的[注]，",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5282,
        "text": "诽谤者，四处造谣者，",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5283,
        "text": "吝啬者[或妨碍行善者]，过分者[超越法度者]，犯罪者，",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5284,
        "text": "残暴者，此外，还有私生子。",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5285,
        "text": "[这是]因为他拥有财富和儿女。",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5286,
        "text": "当有人向他诵读我的启示时，他说：“这只是前人的风俗习惯而已。”",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5287,
        "text": "我将在他的鼻子上打上烙印。",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5288,
        "text": "我必将考验他们，犹如我曾考验果园的人们一样。当时，他们[果园的人们]发誓他们将在[次日]早晨采摘园中的果子，",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5289,
        "text": "但他们没有说：“因沙安拉[假如安拉意欲]！”",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5290,
        "text": "所以，当他们[夜里]正熟睡时，果园遭受了从你的主降示的火灾[并烧毁了]。",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5291,
        "text": "清晨，果园变成了一片焦土。",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5292,
        "text": "早晨，他们互相喊叫：",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5293,
        "text": "“假如你们要采摘[你们的果子]，你们应在早晨到你们的果园去。”",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5294,
        "text": "于是他们便出发了，[途中]他们低声商议说：",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5295,
        "text": "“今天不要让任何贫民进入园中打扰你们。”",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5296,
        "text": "他们早晨[信心百倍地准备]进入果园，[他们]以为他们有能力阻止[贫民进入果园采摘果子]。",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5297,
        "text": "当他们看见果园时，他们才说：“我们的确迷误了，",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5298,
        "text": "不，我们[的水果]被剥夺了。”",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5299,
        "text": "他们中最优秀的人说：“难道我没有告诉过你们吗？你们为什么不说“因沙安拉[假如安拉意欲]呢？”",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5300,
        "text": "他们说：“赞美我们的主超绝！我们确是不义者。”",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5301,
        "text": "于是，他们彼此走来，互相指责。",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5302,
        "text": "他们说；“我们真该死！我们确是悖逆者。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5303,
        "text": "我们的主也许会赐给我们一个比这更好的果园。我们的确归信我们的主了[我们渴望善报，渴望他宽恕我们的罪恶，且在后世赐给我们报酬]。”",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5304,
        "text": "这就是[今世的]刑罚，但后世的刑罚才是最大的，假如他们知道。",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5305,
        "text": "敬畏者在他们的主那里必将获得恩泽的乐园。",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5306,
        "text": "难道我对待穆斯林[归顺者]与对待犯罪者是一样的吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5307,
        "text": "你们怎么啦？你们是怎样判断的？",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5308,
        "text": "难道你们有一部可供你们学习的经典，",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5309,
        "text": "你们的确可从那部经典中获得你们所选择的一切吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5310,
        "text": "难道你们与我订了到复活日才满期的誓约，而你们必将获得你们所判断的吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5311,
        "text": "你问问他们吧！他们谁能为此担保呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5312,
        "text": "难道他们有“许多伙伴[主宰]”吗？假如他们是诚实者，让他们把他们的“伙伴们[主宰]”召来吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5313,
        "text": "当灾难降临，他们被召去叩拜[安拉]的那日[复活日]，他们[伪信者]将无能为力[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5314,
        "text": "他们的目光下垂，羞辱笼罩着他们。[这是因为]他们[在尘世]健全时，他们常被召去叩拜[安拉，如礼拜，但他们不愿意叩拜安拉]。",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5315,
        "text": "你让我惩罚那些否认《古兰经》的人吧！我将在他们不知不觉时逐渐惩罚他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5316,
        "text": "我将暂时宽延他们，我的计划确是强大的。",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5317,
        "text": "难道你[穆圣]向他们索取过[传教的]报酬，他们因纳税而负担太重吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5318,
        "text": "难道他们拥有未见之物[此处特指天经——《受保护的仙牌》]，因而他们能记录下来吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5319,
        "text": "你当耐心等待你的主的判决[注]，你不要像那鱼的伙伴一样：当时，他[鱼的伙伴]非常悲伤地[高声]祈求他的主。",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5320,
        "text": "要是从他的主降示的恩惠没有到达他，那么，[他必定留在鱼腹中，但我宽恕了他]，他必受谴责地被扔到光秃秃的岸边。",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5321,
        "text": "然后，他的主选择他并使他成为善人之一。",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5322,
        "text": "不信仰者听见教诲[《古兰经》]时，他们[憎恶《古兰经》]的目光几乎使你跌倒。他们说：“他[穆圣]确是个疯子。”",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5323,
        "text": "这[《古兰经》]确是对众世界的一项教诲。",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
